  <lyrics>[V1]
 Dios Awquejja
 üñtanitaya,
 Thaquiman sarañsa
 Yanapt'itaya. (Bis)
 
[C]
 Arunacamajj Tatay
 Korits juc'amp sumawa.
 Yatiñamay churita
 Amuyt'ayitay. (Bis)
 
[V2]
 Acapachan
 Nayataquejja
 Korisa kolkesa
 Pist'iriquiwa. (Bis)
 
[V3]
 Ucqha suma
 Pankaranacas
 Inti khanamampejj
 Wañsuquiniwa. (Bis)
 
